title: Studio + 1 unfinished room
posting_body: ['Studio + 1 unfinished room, Wedgewood', '-\tSlate floors in kitchen and bathroom.', '-\tNew carpet in main area.', '-\tBright (3 south facing windows + recessed lighting).', '-\tSeparate entrance.', '-\tDedicated washer/dryer.', '-\tLots of storage.', '-\tLarge fenced yard', '-\tGood parking', 'Its about 500 sq ft total, a studio + an unfinished room.', 'The studio is about 400 sq feet including kitchen, full bath and main area.', 'There is an unfinished room, ~100sq ft, which could function as a gear room (there are some benches), a dark room, an art space, or a large walk in closet.', 'Available Aug 1.', ' $1425/month for rent and all bills (electricity, water, sewer, garbage, heat, high speed internet).', 'Easy parking in front of house.', ' First, last, and $500 deposit.', ' Non-smoking.']
